column5: Anybody been in Narrows area this year? How much snow and ice this year? Fishing? Probably won't get up there this winter but have 3 trips planned for this summer!!
Not a whole lot of snow, but not to bad,ice is 2-3ft in areas.Did well on walleyes and a couple trout last time out in about 30-40ft.D'arcy
Hi,On my web site http://www.justfishontario.com on the Fish Reports page there is under Lake of the Woods a report from Shingwak Lodge in Sioux Narrows. Called Whitefish Bay area. Good luck.Phil
